{"tid":2235624,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"IBM擬分拆出IT設施服務部門成新上市公司 母公司將主營雲端運算業務","createTime":"2020-10-08T23:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T04:23:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a23b33e7b69dedf5dc188832c768fa0529c52905","tid":2235624,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T23:52:58.000Z","msg":"〔編譯楊芙宜／台北報導〕有109年歷史的IBM週四宣布，計畫將公司一分為二，其IT基礎設施服務部門擬分拆出去成為新公司，將以新名上市，明年底前完成分拆；IBM本身將把重心放在高獲利的雲端運算業務。消息傳出，IBM在美股早盤聞訊大漲逾7.8%，來到每股133.73美元。<br />\n<br />\nIBM宣布將展開戰略更新，目標在2021年年底之前完成分拆IT基礎設施服務部門，新公司將專注於客戶基礎架構的管理和現代化；目前該業務仍在IBM的全球技術服務部門底下，服務4600位客戶。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3316089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3316089&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=66ac95f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3316089&h=4da0b89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3316089</a>"},{"pid":"840a747be0d24d0872ab337c2b8e735042b53aa9","tid":2235624,"uid":123860,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"買唔買得過？"},{"pid":"f10a62aacd488a502eeda8613785353d6507e6e0","tid":2235624,"uid":188610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"想知量子電腦研發係跟邊部份?"},{"pid":"45624d382698c8af95727fbbf4fa016c0540e540","tid":2235624,"uid":244958,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"做service個邊拆出去，因為為賺唔到錢，影響盤數"},{"pid":"19b5c2ce64320405531ee06143cd428c6bc2c281","tid":2235624,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f10a62aacd488a502eeda8613785353d6507e6e0","tid":2235624,"uid":188610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"想知量子電腦研發係跟邊部份?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020